ba8a32f0ae9a7f4670fee47738e50424cf29951","tid":405672,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:10:26.000Z","msg":"咁好心機，我又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9640ee7b7ce850abba120d5d7518ced99b65e79","tid":405672,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"屌你落馬蹄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c3e684e2ce6aafe6b207a3a5b62ed68cbb22ba","tid":405672,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"湯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5a34637564080ad3fda6835c4b90663e9f2674","tid":405672,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:22:25.000Z","msg":"有無包法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點包"},{"pid":"6e131501bd9de5b0b9862b3bd60bb89d44154ff2","tid":405672,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2186ac8340056e35c246e33fe127e0855bb9f62f","tid":405672,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"幾驚入黎見到鼻涕紙巾"},{"pid":"8d08068df1479b9ce8ec7863586d8632f2cf6aba","tid":405672,"uid":62856,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"有巴打話想睇包法，所以就食個雲吞做早餐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/110030_1fa714077f6f7eef253bc627d609bebc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F110030_1fa714077f6f7eef253bc627d609bebc.jpg&h=c6d413cc&s={SIZE}\" />首先就當然係準備肉餡，同肉餅好似，肥豬肉一定要夠，唔係就唔會滑，再加上自己鐘意嘅料，蝦，粟米啊等等<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/110532_81d3efdd36f673c1354919cf83301875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F110532_81d3efdd36f673c1354919cf83301875.jpg&h=f34c7847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將肉餡放係底三分一嘅位置<br />\n⼀⼁乛⼀<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/110729_5d8047ab942ccaa945c99b20a6a2d45c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F110729_5d8047ab942ccaa945c99b20a6a2d45c.jpg&h=6d9632df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再向上折到大概一半到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/110809_9733fedc69e3355de27c723af6300196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F110809_9733fedc69e3355de27c723af6300196.jpg&h=1d386155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一般上網教係對折，但咁樣你會食到個皮會厚咗少少，依個人喜好啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/110958_e7246cd0361ab2a1ca0b3c5e27b1e01e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F110958_e7246cd0361ab2a1ca0b3c5e27b1e01e.jpg&h=71f6ea9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最最最重要就係一定要用陰力壓一壓肉個邊位，唔係煮完就會散修修，兩邊都要<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/111204_746f8c0a331909b45f31bfc2a74eb69d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F111204_746f8c0a331909b45f31bfc2a74eb69d.jpg&h=176758a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再打橫對折，同壓<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/111300_11d12897a8aaede44293bbd04dd3d08d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F111300_11d12897a8aaede44293bbd04dd3d08d.jpg&h=50e04eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早餐食9隻就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/111354_24e143190aeb728f6c28bec9e8eac601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F111354_24e143190aeb728f6c28bec9e8eac601.jpg&h=f8f8a264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煮完，食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔壓嘅話，就唔會好似豬腦咁嘅紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nEnjoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b37143330d40b67f394d36ea92a668835786f57","tid":405672,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"小弟只係業餘，有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6a959419f2e959537cc874e381af95ea6273c4","tid":405672,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有巴打話想睇包法，所以就食個雲吞做早餐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/110030_1fa714077f6f7eef253bc627d609bebc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F110030_1fa714077f6f7eef253bc627d609bebc.jpg&h=c6d413cc&s={SIZE}\" />首先就當然係準備肉餡，同肉餅好似，肥豬肉一定要夠，唔係就唔會滑，再加上自己鐘意嘅料，蝦，粟米啊等等<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/110532_81d3efdd36f673c1354919cf83301875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F110532_81d3efdd36f673c1354919cf83301875.jpg&h=f34c7847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將肉餡放係底三分一嘅位置<br />\n⼀⼁乛⼀<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/110729_5d8047ab942ccaa945c99b20a6a2d45c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F110729_5d8047ab942ccaa945c99b20a6a2d45c.jpg&h=6d9632df&